      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jr-Chang Chen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:261px;\"><a href=\"/File:Jr-Chang_Chen.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/59/Jr-Chang_Chen.jpg\" width=\"259\" height=\"259\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Jr-Chang_Chen.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jr-Chang Chen</div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jr-Chang Chen</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientist, game researcher and programmer, and associate professor at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chung_Yuan_Christian_University\">Chung Yuan Christian University</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhongli\">Zhongli City</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taoyuan_County,_Taiwan\">Taoyuan County</a>. Jr-Chang Chen received his B.Sc.,  M.Sc., and Ph.D. degrees in CS and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_engineering\">information engineering</a> from <a href=\"/National_Taiwan_University\" title=\"National Taiwan University\">National Taiwan University</a>, in 1996, 1998, and 2005, respectively <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. He is co-author of the <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> programs and multiple gold medal winners at <a href=\"/Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"Computer Olympiad\">Computer Olympiads</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Contemplation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Contemplation (page does not exist)\">Contemplation</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=ELP&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ELP (page does not exist)\">ELP</a>, and more recently, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chimo (page does not exist)\">Chimo</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, the <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a> program <a href=\"/index.php?title=EVG&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"EVG (page does not exist)\">EVG</a>, and the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurikabe\">Nurikabe</a> puzzle program <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=653\">Enigma</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2001_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2001 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jr-Chang_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2001_...\">2001 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jr-Chang_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2001 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>ELP wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#24_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 24, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">6th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>ELP wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">7th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>ZMBL wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 4</a> &#160;» <a href=\"/8th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"8th Computer Olympiad\">8th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tai-Ning_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tai-Ning Yang (page does not exist)\">Tai-Ning Yang</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/220174553_Computer_Chinese_Chess\">Computer Chinese Chess</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#27_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 27, No. 1</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/223d/ef59c884503f18610bba314034157f55aacd.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jr-Chang_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Handtalk III wins 19x19 Go tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#28_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 28, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/10th_Computer_Olympiad#Go\" title=\"10th Computer Olympiad\">10th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>XQMaster wins Chinese Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#28_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 28, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/10th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"10th Computer Olympiad\">10th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tai-Ning_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tai-Ning Yang (page does not exist)\">Tai-Ning Yang</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1770082\">Study on loop problem in opening database for chinese chess programs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/ieaaie/ieaaie2007.html#YenYCH07\">20. IEA/AIE 2007: Kyoto, Japan</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jian-Yu_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jian-Yu Chen (page does not exist)\">Jian-Yu Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Pangfeng_Liu\" title=\"Pangfeng Liu\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/4085558478885735/\">An Intelligent Tutoring System of Chinese Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/ieaaie/ieaaie2009.html#ChenCCHLH09\">IEA/AIE 2009</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>TMSK wins the Chinese-Chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#32_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 32, No. 2</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/14th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"14th Computer Olympiad\">14th Computer Olympiad</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jr-Chang_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Shi-Yuan_Chiu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Shi-Yuan Chiu (page does not exist)\">Shi-Yuan Chiu</a>, <a href=\"/Cheng-Wei_Chou\" title=\"Cheng-Wei Chou\">Cheng-Wei Chou</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Cpuzzler wins Nonogram Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#34_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 34, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/15th_Computer_Olympiad#Nonogram\" title=\"15th Computer Olympiad\">15th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ming-Cheng_Cheng&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ming-Cheng Cheng (page does not exist)\">Ming-Cheng Cheng</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsan-Cheng_Su&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tsan-Cheng Su (page does not exist)\">Tsan-Cheng Su</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Shiga wins Chinese Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#35_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 35, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/16th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"16th Computer Olympiad\">16th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Cheng-Wei_Chou\" title=\"Cheng-Wei Chou\">Cheng-Wei Chou</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"