i-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tsan-Cheng_Su&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tsan-Cheng Su (page does not exist)\">Tsan-Cheng Su</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>SHIGA Wins Chinese Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Wen-Jie_Tseng\" title=\"Wen-Jie Tseng\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (<b>2013</b>).  <i>DARKNIGHT Wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wen-Jie_Tseng\" title=\"Wen-Jie Tseng\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lung-Ping_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lung-Ping Chen (page does not exist)\">Lung-Ping Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>TCGA 2013 Computer Game Tournaments</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Multilevel Inference in Chinese Chess Endgame Knowledge Bases</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_4\" title=\"ICGA J